{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SetupAutomation"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SetupAutomation"},{"text":" provides version-specific keyboard input sequences","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that walk through the macOS Setup Assistant without any human","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"interaction. After the sequence completes, the VM has:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A user account (configurable, defaults to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"text":"\/","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SSH (Remote Login) enabled"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A UTC timezone configured","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Design","anchor":"Design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This follows the approach pioneered by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/cirruslabs\/tart","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" for Packer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"boot_command"},{"type":"text","text":" automation. The sequences have been verified against"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Tart’s working Packer plugin and adapted for direct use via the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Virtualization framework’s keyboard API."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Requirements","anchor":"Requirements","type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content"